== 製作 ==
=== 開發與製作 ===
[[File:13_Reasons_Why_opening.png|thumb]]
在閱讀{{le|傑伊·艾夏|Jay Asher}}著作之人氣小說《[[漢娜的遺言|-{zh-hant:漢娜的遺言;zh-hans:十三个理由;}-]]》後，[[赛琳娜·戈麦斯|赛琳娜·戈麦斯]]與其母親曼蒂·提費（{{lang|en|Mandy Teefey}}）及製作人克莉絲朵·雷布林（{{lang|en|Kristel Laiblin}}）將其推銷至{{le|匿名內容|Anonymous Content}}，以開發影視版本。<ref name="Variety"/>[[環球影業|環球影業]]於2011年2月8日取得電影翻拍版權，並預定由赛琳娜擔任女主角{{le|漢娜·貝克|Hannah Baker}}。<ref>{{cite web|last=Schwartz|first=Terri|title=Selena Gomez To Star In '13 Reasons Why': Movie, adapted from Jay Asher's young adult novel, looks back at a girl's reasons for committing suicide.|work=[[音樂電視網|MTV News]]|date=2011-02-09|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1657538/selena-gomez-13-reasons-why.jhtml|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2012-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419040926/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1657538/selena-gomez-13-reasons-why.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年10月29日，宣布[[Netflix|Netflix]]將開發電視劇版本，並直接給予本劇13集系列預訂，試播集劇本是由獲得[[普利策獎|普立茲獎]]與[[托尼獎|東尼獎]]肯定的{{le|布萊恩·佑奇|Brian Yorkey}}執筆身兼執行製作，匿名內容與{{le|派拉蒙電視公司|Paramount Television}}共同製作之，而赛琳娜、提費、雷布林與喬伊·戈曼·威托斯（{{lang|en|Joy Gorman Wettels}}）、{{le|邁克爾·蘇格|Michael Sugar}}及{{le|史提夫·高林|Steve Golin}}皆將共同擔任執行製作。<ref name="Variety">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/selena-gomez-13-reasons-why-netflix-1201620194/|title=Netflix Adapting ‘13 Reasons Why’ Into Selena Gomez Series (EXCLUSIVE)|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|author=Elizabeth Wagmeister|date=2015-10-29|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108130140/https://variety.com/2015/tv/news/selena-gomez-13-reasons-why-netflix-1201620194/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Netflix Gives Selena Gomez's '13 Reasons Why' Straight-To-Series Order|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/netflix-gives-selena-gomez-13-reasons-why-straight-to-series-order-1201597481/|website=Deadline|date=2015-10-29|language=en|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2019-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190425181751/https://deadline.com/2015/10/netflix-gives-selena-gomez-13-reasons-why-straight-to-series-order-1201597481/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年2月25日，宣布憑《[[驚爆焦點|驚爆焦點]]》榮獲[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]的[[湯瑪士·麥卡錫|湯姆·麥卡錫]]將執導首兩集，並同時身兼執行製作。<ref name=mccarthy>{{cite web|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|title=Spotlight's Tom McCarthy To Direct & Produce Selena Gomez's Netflix Series '13 Reasons Why' From Paramount TV|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/spotlight-tom-mccarthy-direct-selena-gomez-13-reasons-why-netflix-1201708767/|work=Deadline|date=2016-02-25|accessdate=2016-07-19|archive-date=2016-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711234328/http://deadline.com/2016/02/spotlight-tom-mccarthy-direct-selena-gomez-13-reasons-why-netflix-1201708767/|dead-url=no}}</ref>隔日，宣布《[[美式懸罪|美式懸罪]]》{{le|黛安娜·孫|Diana Son}}加入執行製作陣容，並與佑奇共同擔任[[節目統籌|節目統籌]]。<ref>{{cite web|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|title=Diana Son Joins Selena Gomez's Netflix Series '13 Reasons Why' As Showrunner|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/diana-son-jselena-gomez-netflix-series-13-reasons-showrunner-1201709770/|work=Deadline|date=2016-02-26|accessdate=2016-09-16|archive-date=2016-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917075908/http://deadline.com/2016/02/diana-son-jselena-gomez-netflix-series-13-reasons-showrunner-1201709770/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年5月7日，官方正式宣布續訂第2季13集，而佑奇將繼續擔任節目統籌。<ref name="Season 2">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/13ReasonsWhy/status/861234041370034176/video/1|title=Their story isn't over. Season 2 of #13ReasonsWhy is coming.|author=13 Reasons Why|date=2017-05-07|work=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|accessdate=2017-05-07|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507154400/https://twitter.com/13ReasonsWhy/status/861234041370034176/video/1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Season 2 Variety">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/13-reasons-why-renewed-season-2-netflix-2-1202411389/|title=‘13 Reasons Why’ Renewed for a Second Season at Netflix|author=綜藝雜誌團隊|date=2017-05-07|work=綜藝雜誌|accessdate=2017-05-07|archive-date=2019-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426162546/https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/13-reasons-why-renewed-season-2-netflix-2-1202411389/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年6月6日，Netflix正式宣布續訂第3季13集，同樣由佑奇擔任節目統籌。<ref name="Season 3">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/06/13-reasons-why-renewed-season-3-netflix-1202404504/|title=‘13 Reasons Why’ Renewed For Season 3 By Netflix|work=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2018-06-06|accessdate=2018-06-06|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109025537/https://deadline.com/2018/06/13-reasons-why-renewed-season-3-netflix-1202404504/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

