=== 拍攝 ===
本劇在2016年夏天於[[北加利福尼亞州|北加利福尼亞州]]進行拍攝。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/2016/06/24/selena-gomez-produced-netflix-series-shooting-in-marin-brings-economic-benefits/|title=Selena Gomez-produced Netflix series shooting in Marin brings economic benefits|last=Mara|first=Janis|date=2016-06-24|website=The Mercury News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211081745/http://www.mercurynews.com/2016/06/24/selena-gomez-produced-netflix-series-shooting-in-marin-brings-economic-benefits/|archive-date=2017-02-11|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-02-10}}</ref>第2季於2017年6月14日開拍。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/860730/13-reasons-why-season-2-officially-underway-get-your-first-look|title=''13 Reasons Why'' Season 2 Officially Underway: Get Your First Look|author=Billy Nilles|date=2017-06-14|work=綜藝雜誌|accessdate=2017-06-15|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211203922/http://www.eonline.com/news/860730/13-reasons-why-season-2-officially-underway-get-your-first-look|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 評價 ==
本劇第1季獲得電視影評家廣泛的好評。於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中，獲得85%的新鮮度、平均得分7.3/10（39名評論家），評論家共識：「《漢娜的遺言》用成熟的敘事從YA類型作品中突出，以細膩審視青少年憂鬱的方式，補足了原著。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/13_reasons_why/s01|title=13 Reasons Why: Season 1|publisher=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|accessdate=2017-04-27|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422043543/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/13_reasons_why/s01|dead-url=no}}</ref>於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，獲得了76分（滿分100；17名評論家），屬普遍的好評。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/13-reasons-why|title=13 Reasons Why - Season 1 Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2017-04-27|archive-date=2017-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170406055505/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/13-reasons-why|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本劇在播出後獲得極大的迴響，〈[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]〉評論家莫琳·萊恩（{{lang|en|Maureen Ryan}}）寫道：「一個能抓住多數觀眾直到結束的懸念故事。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/tv/reviews/13-reasons-why-review-netflix-selena-gomez-dylan-minnette-katherine-langford-1202013547/|title=TV Review: ‘13 Reasons Why’ on Netflix|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|author=Maureen Ryan|date=2017-03-21|accessdate=2017-05-08|archive-date=2017-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918014725/http://variety.com/2017/tv/reviews/13-reasons-why-review-netflix-selena-gomez-dylan-minnette-katherine-langford-1202013547/|dead-url=no}}</ref>本劇在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上更累積了超過1100萬則推文，榮登2017年獲得最多推文關注的影集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/netflix-13-reasons-why-twitter-most-popular-show-2017-1202392460/|title=Netflix’s ‘13 Reasons Why’ Is Most Tweeted About Show of 2017 (EXCLUSIVE)|publisher=綜藝雜誌|author=Elizabeth Wagmeister|date=2015-04-21|accessdate=2017-05-08|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113054035/https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/netflix-13-reasons-why-twitter-most-popular-show-2017-1202392460/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第2季評價不如第1季，於爛番茄整合的評論中，僅獲得37%的新鮮度、平均得分5.83/10（19名評論家），評論家共識：「在脫離原作的情況下，《漢娜的遺言》可以更深入探索精心設計的角色；不幸的是，在這個過程中，它失去了節目原先引人入勝的軌跡。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/13_reasons_why/s02|title=13 Reasons Why: Season 2|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2018-05-18|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130171536/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/13_reasons_why/s02|dead-url=no}}</ref>於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，獲得了50分（滿分100；13名評論家），屬好壞參半的評價。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/13-reasons-why/season-2|title=13 Reasons Why - Season 2 Reviews|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2018-05-18|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215201240/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/13-reasons-why/season-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>

